description: Bianca`s Chaoboo was first seen being sent out by Bianca to battle against the wild Chillarmy that Bel wanted to capture. Chillarmy beat Choaboo by tickling it with its tail. Bianca`s Chaoboo battle Ash`s Pikachu but it wasn`t strong enough to win as Pikachu`s Volt Tackle was too strong for it.
name: Chaoboo (Bel)
